snippet.title: The Caribbean Sail - Fantasy Toggle
snippet.description:
The most whimsical 8-bit game about sailing the world now has a fantasy mode!

Discover new legendary locations! 

Get devoured by a kraken!

Unlock nine new ships and seven new professions!

Pursue four new storylines!

Full expansion log: https://victorianclambake.com/logbook/2020/6/16/the-caribbean-sail-v17
